body.description: You want what's best for baby, and that means adding fresh fruits, vegetables and purees to the mealtime mix. The Munchkin Fresh Food Feeder allows your little one to enjoy delicious finger foods without giving you cause for concern. With its simple mesh design, this handy teething feeder allows for babies to gnaw on foods safely. Simply place a piece of fruit, vegetable or even meat into the mesh bag and snap it shut. Baby can chew, suck and taste the whole food goodness, with only small, digestible pieces coming through - reducing the risk of choking. It's also a smart alternative to a teething toy. The Fresh Food Feeder features a colorful, easy-grip handle for your little one to hold - making this his first real step toward feeding independence

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on July 16, 2021
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars My kids love this
reviews.reviewText: I used this product with my first child when he was a baby- he loved being able to experience new foods & I loved that this was a safer way to let him experience new tastes while preventing choking. I bought this product again, for my daughter. She had no difficulty holding onto the grip piece! My kids love this & I would say it helps with teething. Only draw back is the mess they make between the drool and juices from the fruits we put in them! Product is fairly easy to clean.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 23, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for first foods
reviews.reviewText: My daughter loves these they are the perfect size for her to hold onto and eat her favorite fruits and veggies! They have a nice selection of colors as well.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 18, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars These are great for teething babies!
reviews.reviewText: I love this. I put strawberries/raspberries in them and stick them in the freezer and give them to my daughter to suck on. She loves them. They’re also really nice for just fruit in general even before your kiddo has a lot of teeth because they can suck the fruit through the net.

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 29, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Awesome for baby MESSY for mom
reviews.reviewText: My baby loves this, she has so much fun feeding herself. It is just a nightmare to clean. It takes a lot of scrubbing and turning inside out and back. You really got it get in there to clean it all out. It took alot to clean and I am dreading using it often BUT the baby loves it so much so I am willing to suffer through the cleaning process. Also you will basically have to Bath the baby after because it is going to get everywhere 😅

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on February 8, 2024
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Bite-sized Bliss: Baby's Fruit Feeder Delight
reviews.reviewText: The fresh fruit feeder for my baby is a game-changer! Watching her delight in the mango squeezing out with every bite is pure joy. It's a safe way for her to enjoy various fruits, just like her sisters. However, my only complaint is that cleaning the inside can be a bit challenging. Despite this, the joy it brings to my baby's face makes it a worthwhile addition to our feeding routine.
